# TruffleHog ignore patterns for the Gridltd fleet.
#
# One regex per line. Lines starting with # are comments.
# Tested via `trufflehog filesystem . --exclude-paths .trufflehogignore`.
#
# Sister to `.gitleaks.toml`'s `[allowlist].paths` for security-test-
# fixture files that intentionally contain synthetic patterns shaped
# like real secrets — `__tests__/*-guard.test.js` and similar test
# files. Same scoping intent.

# Security-test-fixture files (tests for outbound-guard.test.js et al.)
__tests__/[^/]*-guard\.test\.(js|ts|jsx|tsx)
